"  :menuselection:`Ventas --> Productos --> Listas de precios`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:433
msgid ""
"From the :guilabel:`Pricelists` page, select a desired pricelist to modify, "
